      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "NANGAR MCGRAW (2) boasts a strong record this journey with eight wins and four minors from 17 tries. Recorded a 7 length win (19.81) in a Grade 4/5 last time at this track. Looks well placed and should feature. SOUL OF FIRE (4) is a smart dog who pinged the lids and led throughout to win (19.87) at this track in Grade 5 over 350m. Has a strong winning record at this journey. Ran the fastest time on the program in her latest win. One of the key runners again. ANNIHILATING (8) was unfancied latest when jumping from this same draw but belied the odds to place (20.15) over 350m at this track in a NG. Safe beginner but wide box to overcome and will need some luck. Key chance on best form. FEDERAL SNIPER (5) is a last start winner and can go on with it.",
